summary: Become Villain In The Game Cultivation A professional player that died tragically while playing a game, got transmigrated into the game itself! Whilst the villain who tragically died under the swords of thousands of players in the game. In a dark coffin, bereft of light and water, he awakened the system, and received a newcomer’s gift package containing 10,000 Spiritual Points! The same tragic life, yet is now the beginning of a counterattack! Kicking the coffin board open, reciting mantras, leveling up like crazy, and collecting the world’s best beauties one by one! In this one hell of a broken script, watch how he meets and slays the gods, and mock the game’s creator!
